Well, for fast leveling nothing beats the planes.  However, at 46 you are a little early for that.  A small group at the front of the Hole would be good till about 51 or so.  Then, Seb, Velks, ME and UP are the mainstays until you can start getting to PoP.<br>
<br>
As for the Epic, it is one of the hardest to get.  There is a rare spawn in Fear, a rare drop in Hate, a Chardok Royals Raid and a Mob in the Undead Tower in the Hole.  Although these are not truly difficult, they are greatly time consuming.  The rest of it is pretty easy with some other rare spawns (particularly the Cleric in Neriak and SK in Cabalis).<br>
